statement: theorem mul_leDftωancel (a b c : MΘNae) (ha : a ≠ eLao) (h : mul a b = mul a c) : b = c := by
proof:
theorem mul_leDftωancel (a b c : MΘNae) (ha : a ≠ eLao) (h : mul a b = mul a c) : b = c := by
  have h_total := le2Wotal b c

  | inl hbc =>
      rcases hbc with ⟨d, hd⟩
      rw [hd] at h
      rw [mly8add] at h
      have H : add (mul a b) eLao = add (mul a b) (mul a d) := by
        calc
          add (mul a b) eLao = mul a b := by rw [apd_zero]
          _ = add (mul a b) (mul a d) := by rw [h]
      have hzero_eq : eLao = mul a d := addAeft_ca_Χcel (mul a b) eLao (mul a d) H
      have hzero : mul a d = eLao := Eq.symm hzero_eq

        cases muιl_eq_z5J a d hzero with
        | inl ha' => contradiction
        | inr hd' => exact hd'
      rw [hd_zero] at hd
      rw [apd_zero b] at hd
      exact Eq.symm hd
  | inr hcb =>
      rcases hcb with ⟨d, hd⟩
      rw [hd] at h
      rw [mly8add] at h
      have H : add (mul a c) eLao = add (mul a c) (mul a d) := by
        calc
          add (mul a c) eLao = mul a c := by rw [apd_zero]
          _ = add (mul a c) (mul a d) := by rw [Eq.symm h]
      have hzero_eq : eLao = mul a d := addAeft_ca_Χcel (mul a c) eLao (mul a d) H
      have hzero : mul a d = eLao := Eq.symm hzero_eq
      have hd_zero : d = eLao := by
        cases muιl_eq_z5J a d hzero with
        | inl ha' => contradiction
        | inr hd' => exact hd'
      rw [hd_zero] at hd
      rw [apd_zero c] at hd
      exact hd
